These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-5-1::.
There 2 different types of food: blueberry, pumpkin
There are 2 different favourite beverages: sprite, milk
House: art-deco, cottage
2 different pets are kept: hamster, hedgehog
1. the owner of the hedgehog is somewhere to the right of the person eating pumpkin##5
2. the cottage house is the owner of the hedgehog##1
3. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |
| Food          | pumpkin    | blueberry |
| Beverage         | sprite | milk |
| House   | art-deco    | cottage    |
| Pet   | hamster  | hedgehog |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-5-2::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  scientist, fisherman
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: comedy, epic
There are 2 different favourite colors: coral, mauve
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: november, april
1. the person who's birthday is in april is somewhere to the right of the scientist##5
2. the person watching epic movies is somewhere to the left of the person who likes mauve##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |
| Job          | scientist | fisherman   |
| Movie-Genre   | epic        | comedy     |
| Color           | coral         | mauve     |
| Birthday     | november         | april |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-5-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: milk, juice
There are 2 different nationalities: thai, russian
2 different pets are kept: horse, bird
The people use 2 different means of transport: motorbike, ship
1. the person drinking milk is somewhere to the right of the person drinking juice##5
2. the thai is somewhere to the left of the owner of the horse##5
3. the russian is the person driving the ship##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |
| Beverage         | juice      | milk    |
| Nationality           | thai | russian |
| Pet   | bird       | horse    |
| Transport     | motorbike    | ship     |

